data.description: Don't miss this great opportunity to live in the highly sought-after Northpointe neighborhood.  A beautiful front porch, with room for seating welcomes you to a home that boasts plenty of character.  It features beautiful arched doorways and windows throughout and is freshly painted and ready for its new owners!  The large kitchen is open to the living area and perfect for open entertaining and has direct access to the backyard.  The living room features a brick corner fireplace.  Don't miss the large primary suite with a large walk-in closet as well as an open bonus flex space that could be office or nursery.  Brand new luxury vinyl plank flooring downstairs as well as all new carpet upstairs!  There are three single-car garages with a large driveway for additional parking.  THIS HOME ALSO QUALIFIES FOR SPECIAL FINANCING!
